high_descs: While facing the round gray table turn to your left and walk to the counter with the microwave on it across the room.
Pick up the pepper shaker located on the counter to the left side and to the front of the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the gray table, stand to the right of the chair at the table.
Place the shaker on the table on the side where a white mug with a fork to its left is.
Turn and walk to the white countertop with a toaster on it and to the left of the stove.
Pick up the pepper shaker located to the left front of the toaster.
Turn to your left and walk to the gray table and stand to the right of the chair.
Place the pepper shaker on the table to the left of the first shaker and in front of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two pepper shakers in different areas of the kitchen, place them on the table

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, go around the counter and keep going forward to the counter to the left of the microwave.
Take the pepper from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn left at the round black table.
Put the pepper in front of the mug on the table.
Turn left, go forward, go around the counter with the toaster, then turn left to face the counter.
Take the pepper from the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn left at the round black table.
Put the pepper in front of the lettuce on the left of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two pepper mills on a table.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, go around the corner, keep going forward to the counter to the left of the microwave.
Take the pepper mill from the counter.
Turn around, go forward past the end of the counter, turn left at the round black table.
Put the pepper mill on the table in front of the fork and mug.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the pepper mill from the counter.
Turn right, go back to the round black table.
Put the pepper mill in front of the closest lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put two pepper mills on a table.
